description: Stony's Pizza is a father-son business started in Austin, TX in September '07. The food truck also caters for orders no less than $150. Also, for private parties we roll right up into your driveway and make pizzas to order, hot and fresh, right out of the oven. No less than $200 per party, prices vary according to number of people being fed. Doing our best to keep Austin weird!! Give us a call and order some pie!!!
name: Stony's Pizza
